{"Id":687941,"Title":"和陶诗 劝农","Dynasty":"明","Author":"李贤（原德","Context":"夫古后稷，伟哉哲人。树艺五谷，乃得其真。教民稼穑，万世相因。菜羹必祭，粒我生人。舜有五臣，莫贤于稷。躬稼既勤，庶类乃殖。启我后人，服田力穑。万世赖之，惟此艰食。旦旦胥征，载隰载陆。零雨既收，淑气乃穆。布谷催耕，千耦相逐。日既入矣，不遑归宿。惟农之业，可以恒久。贤者避世，亦惟耕耦。嗟尔士女，尽力南亩。租税莫逃，勿为游手。力田乃丰，不勤则匮。舍此为生，衣食何冀。譬之学奕，而思鸿至。俯仰之间，求无斯愧。樊迟愿学，圣门相鄙。士农异业，勿乖所履。各思其位，莫出其轨。农或士习，乃就厥美。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"c0749cd98e0b2c83bea283c4360bf5d5","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6173029,"Sentence":"力田乃丰，不勤则匮。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lì tián nǎi fēng ，bú qǐn zé kuì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":16,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173030,"Sentence":"舍此为生，衣食何冀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shě ci wéi shēng ，yī shǐ hé jì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":17,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173031,"Sentence":"譬之学奕，而思鸿至。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"pì zhī xué yì ，ér sāi hóng zhì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":18,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173032,"Sentence":"俯仰之间，求无斯愧。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fǔ yǎng zhī jiān ，qǐu mó sī kuì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":19,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173033,"Sentence":"樊迟愿学，圣门相鄙。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fán chǐ yuàn xué ，shèng mén xiāng bi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":20,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173034,"Sentence":"士农异业，勿乖所履。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shì nóng yì yè ，wù guāi suǒ lǚ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":21,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173035,"Sentence":"各思其位，莫出其轨。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gě sāi jī wèi ，mò chū jī gui ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":22,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173036,"Sentence":"农或士习，乃就厥美。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"nóng huò shì xǐ ，nǎi jìu jué měi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":23,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6173013,"Sentence":"夫古后稷，伟哉哲人。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fū gǔ hòu jì ，wěi zāi zhé rén ","Tag":null,"